# 💰 Creator Profit Tracker

A simple and customizable income & expense tracker built for creators, small businesses, and side hustlers.

Track your money, organize categories, and understand your profits — all in one clean interface.

---

## 🚀 Live Demo
👉 https://YOUR-USERNAME.github.io/creator-profit-tracker/

