---

## ✨ Features

- ✅ Add income and expenses
- 📊 Automatic profit calculation
- 🗂️ Custom categories (add & delete your own)
- 🔍 Filter transactions by category
- 📈 Category breakdown analytics
- 💾 Saves data locally (no login required)
- 📤 Export transactions to CSV
- ⚡ Fast, lightweight, and easy to use

---

## 💡 Why This App?

Most finance trackers are:
- Too complicated
- Not built for creators
- Overloaded with features you don’t need

This app is designed to be:
✔ Simple  
✔ Customizable  
✔ Focused on real-world creator income  

Perfect for:
- Etsy sellers
- Amazon FBA sellers
- Freelancers
- Side hustlers

---

## 🛠️ Built With

- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript
- Web Storage API (localStorage)

---

## 📦 How to Use

1. Download or clone the repo
2. Open `index.html` in your browser
3. Start adding your income and expenses

No installation or setup required.

